382
00:25:30,710 --> 00:25:31,990
in your world.

383
00:25:32,510 --> 00:25:33,510
As a player, one of the steps

384
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,790
in Si Yan's hidden task

385
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:37,550
