516
00:32:07,390 --> 00:32:07,990
You

517
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:09,390
and I

518
00:32:11,470 --> 00:32:12,270
are both unreal.

519
00:32:17,190 --> 00:32:19,430
If we are characters in a play, that'll be nice.

520
00:32:20,150 --> 00:32:21,110
Because in plays,

521
00:32:21,550 --> 00:32:23,750
