550
00:34:47,350 --> 00:34:48,830
I was making things up.

551
00:34:48,830 --> 00:34:49,790
Did you believe all that?

552
00:34:50,190 --> 00:34:50,830
I did,

553
00:34:52,389 --> 00:34:53,469
