557
00:35:03,630 --> 00:35:04,630
You can go wherever you want.

558
00:35:05,630 --> 00:35:06,550
It is also so tiny that

559
00:35:06,950 --> 00:35:08,590
all you need is a cell phone

560
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:10,510
